// tool/anima_void_claim_drift_cycle39_audit.hexa — cycle 77 void claim drift는 cycle 39 false alarm 판명 (raw#9 hexa-only).
//
// PURPOSE
//   memory project_workspace.md (cycle 69)에 "void claim drift (100% vs 0.3%)"
